{
  "texts": [
    "Most of the preceding models can forecast certain basic scenes successfully.",
    "Thus, future studies may begin with delicate circumstances, while the accuracy of prediction will be increased if the probability distribution of dynamic scenes can be modeled and predicted.",
    "Deep CNNs have demonstrated strong performance on data with a grid-like topology or that is time series in nature.",
    "However, in real-world applications, deep CNN architectures have run into additional difficulties.",
    "The different researchers have fascinating discussions about CNN's performance on different machine learning tasks."
  ]
}